KRL / Laser Synthesis
DEF GOLD_CHAIN_PROCESS()
  INI_ROBOT()
  $VEL.CP = 0.06
  LASER_PWR = 95.0
  WELD_FREQ = 120
  FOR i = 1 TO 87
    GRIP_LINK(i)
    MOVE_TO_WELD_POS()
    START_SHIELD_GAS(ARGON)
    LASER_ON()
    LIN_REL {X 0.1}
    LASER_OFF()
  ENDFOR
END
Feed Rate 280 mm/min
Laser Pwr 95.0 W
